hyprland-undercover (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Features:
    - One-click toggle between Hyprland and Windows 11 look
    - Windows 11-style Waybar taskbar
    - Windows 11-style Rofi/Wofi start menu
    - GTK4/Libadwaita settings application
    - Automatic backup and restore of configurations
    - Multi-distro installer support

